<blockquote><p>90% of us stop working on our new year's resolutions by week 1. Today is exactly a week into 2024. If you are among us, I built a 30 min actionable piece to get back on track. And as a subscriber you now have acccess to it.</p></blockquote><div><hr></div><p>Firstly stop following really long goal trackers. All you need is weekly rituals jotted on a recurring Google Calendar, period. The 3 themes I personally chase.<br><br><strong>#1 Wealth goal &#128176; (10 mins)</strong><br>This includes planning how much income you will make this year. What needs to go into savings, spending, building assets &amp; managing liabilities this year. A simple question and answer format (I will share the template) that helps you understand your money goal for 2024. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc3fe4ce4-67ff-40a8-a08a-7a81e78ec5f9_566x663.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc3fe4ce4-67ff-40a8-a08a-7a81e78ec5f9_566x663.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc3fe4ce4-67ff-40a8-a08a-7a81e78ec5f9_566x663.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc3fe4ce4-67ff-40a8-a08a-7a81e78ec5f9_566x663.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2